alerts.description:
There is a risk of persistent rain (Level 2 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: 50-70 l/m²; in windward areas: < 90 l/m²

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 800 m; Max. gusts: 60-80 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 90 km/h

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Height range: > 200 m; Max. gusts: < 60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 75 km/h
